{
  "name": "RNA-seq Differential Expression Pipeline",
  "description": "四步分析流程：预处理、差异表达、富集分析、可视化报告",
  "dataset": "dataset:expr_matrix_raw",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "preprocess",
      "name": "数据预处理",
      "description": "过滤低表达基因，归一化",
      "input": [
        "expr_matrix_raw",
        "sample_group"
      ],
      "output": "preprocessed_matrix",
      "tool": {
        "name": "fastp + DESeq2 vst",
        "command": "Rscript preprocess.R --input {input} --output {output}",
        "expected_output": "normalized_counts.csv"
      },
      "llm_prompt": "给定以下表达矩阵（原始counts）和样本分组，请推荐低表达基因的过滤阈值（如CPM>1）并解释理由。矩阵：{expression_summary}",
      "llm_output_format": "文本建议"
    },
    {
      "id": "diff_exp",
      "name": "差异表达分析",
      "description": "识别对照组与处理组间的差异表达基因",
      "input": [
        "preprocessed_matrix",
        "sample_group"
      ],
      "output": "diff_results",
      "tool": {
        "name": "DESeq2",
        "command": "Rscript deseq2.R --input {input} --group {group} --output {output}",
        "expected_output": "diff_genes.csv"
      },
      "llm_prompt": "以下是预处理后的基因表达矩阵（每组均值）：Control组：{ctrl_means}，Treatment组：{treat_means}。请根据这些数值判断哪些基因可能显著差异表达（上调或下调），并说明理由。返回格式：基因名，变化方向，简要理由。",
      "llm_output_format": "JSON列表"
    },
    {
      "id": "enrich",
      "name": "功能富集分析",
      "description": "对差异基因进行GO/KEGG富集分析",
      "input": [
        "diff_results"
      ],
      "output": "enrich_results",
      "tool": {
        "name": "clusterProfiler",
        "command": "Rscript enrich.R --genelist {input} --output {output}",
        "expected_output": "enrichment.csv"
      },
      "llm_prompt": "差异基因列表：{gene_list}。请根据生物学知识（如KEGG通路、GO术语）推测这些基因可能富集在哪些通路或功能，并给出理由。",
      "llm_output_format": "文本描述"
    },
    {
      "id": "report",
      "name": "可视化与报告生成",
      "description": "生成火山图、富集柱状图和总结报告",
      "input": [
        "diff_results",
        "enrich_results"
      ],
      "output": "final_report",
      "tool": {
        "name": "ggplot2 + RMarkdown",
        "command": "Rscript report.R --diff {diff} --enrich {enrich} --output {output}",
        "expected_output": "report.html"
      },
      "llm_prompt": "基于以下分析结果撰写一份简要的科研报告摘要：差异基因：{diff_summary}，富集通路：{enrich_summary}。包括主要发现和潜在生物学意义。",
      "llm_output_format": "Markdown文本"
    }
  ],
  "dependencies": [
    {
      "from": "diff_exp",
      "to": "preprocess"
    },
    {
      "from": "enrich",
      "to": "diff_exp"
    },
    {
      "from": "report",
      "to": "diff_exp"
    },
    {
      "from": "report",
      "to": "enrich"
    }
  ]
}